ttyd_index.html.gz is a compiled web client built from ttyd (served by this
plugin via `ttyd -I`). Source repo: https://github.com/tsl0922/ttyd

ttyd is MIT-licensed; its license is reproduced verbatim below. The compiled
bundle also embeds third-party JavaScript libraries under their own licenses
(xterm.js and addons, preact, decko, trzsz, file-saver, whatwg-fetch -- all MIT;
zmodem.js -- Apache-2.0). See ttyd's html/package.json for exact versions.

